Package com.vmware.vapi.protocol.client.http

Interface RequestPreProcessor

  • public interface RequestPreProcessor
    Request pre-processor. Implementation of this interface can modify the compiled HttpRequest that will be used for invoking the REST operation. Example for this is an authentication processor.

        Pre-process HttpRequest before sending it to the caller.

        Exceptions thrown from this method will be ignored.

        Parameters:
        serviceId - service identifier; must not be null
        operationId - operation identifier; must not be null
        request - that will be processed; must not be null
        params - with which the operation will be called; must not be null
        executionContext - for the operation invocation; must not be null
        Returns:
        processed HttpRequest.
